---
import MarketingLayout from '../components/layout/MarketingLayout.astro'
---

<MarketingLayout title="Tentang Kami">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          Tentang Kami
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900">
          Tentang ManggaKu
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Platform marketplace digital yang menghubungkan petani mangga Indramayu langsung dengan konsumen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Misi -->
      <div class="mb-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white rounded-3xl border border-primary-100">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Misi Kami</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          ManggaKu hadir untuk menjembatani petani mangga di Indramayu dengan konsumen di seluruh Indonesia.
          Kami percaya bahwa petani berhak mendapatkan harga yang adil, dan konsumen berhak mendapatkan
          mangga berkualitas dengan harga transparan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Mengapa Indramayu -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Mengapa Indramayu?</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
          Indramayu adalah salah satu sentra penghasil mangga terbesar di Jawa Barat. Dengan varietas unggulan
          seperti Gedong Gincu, Harum Manis, dan Cengkir, mangga Indramayu memiliki cita rasa yang khas dan
          diminati oleh pasar nasional. Namun, banyak petani yang masih terjebak dalam rantai tengkulak
          dengan harga yang tidak adil.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-6">
          <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Gedong Gincu</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Varietas unggulan khas Indramayu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-600">Harum Manis</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Manis, wangi, dan segar</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-neutral-100 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Cengkir</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Cocok untuk olahan dan ekspor</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tim Kami -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            Tim Kami
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900">
            Kenali Tim ManggaKu
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-500 max-w-md mx-auto">
            Mahasiswa Technopreneurship POLINDRA yang berkomitmen untuk kemajuan petani lokal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
          <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/avataaars/svg?seed=BungaPurwaningsih&backgroundColor=ffdfbf" alt="Bunga Purwaningsih" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-primary-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" width={64} height={64} />
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Bunga Purwaningsih</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-primary-600 mt-1">Frontend Developer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/avataaars/svg?seed=ChairaniNayu&backgroundColor=c0aede" alt="Chairani Nayu Nainggolan" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-secondary-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" width={64} height={64} />
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Chairani Nayu Nainggolan</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary-600 mt-1">UI/UX Designer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/avataaars/svg?seed=DaryIbrahim&backgroundColor=b6e3f4" alt="Dary Ibrahim Akram" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-primary-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" width={64} height={64} />
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Dary Ibrahim Akram</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-primary-600 mt-1">Fullstack Developer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/avataaars/svg?seed=MuhammadReza&backgroundColor=b6e3f4" alt="Muhammad Reza Fadillah" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-secondary-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" width={64} height={64} />
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Muhammad Reza Fadillah</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-secondary-600 mt-1">Backend Developer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            <img src="https://api.dicebear.com/9.x/avataaars/svg?seed=MuhammadRijal&backgroundColor=b6e3f4" alt="Muhammad Rijal Marzuq" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-primary-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" width={64} height={64} />
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-sm">Muhammad Rijal Marzuq</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-primary-600 mt-1">DevOps & QA</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">
            Technopreneurship <span class="font-semibold text-primary-600">POLINDRA</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
